  { time: '11:30', text: 'Cancels a coffee with Jean because parking is difficult and she does not feel confident driving.' },
  { time: '13:00', text: 'Lunch. Beans on toast. Eating in the same chair she has sat in for 30 years.' },
  { time: '15:00', text: 'The boiler makes that noise again. She does not know who to call. David always handled that.' },
  { time: '17:00', text: 'Watches television. Heating only the living room because the rest of the house is too expensive to warm.' },
  { time: '19:30', text: 'Locks up. Checks every door twice. The garden backs onto an alley and she heard something last week.' },
  { time: '21:00', text: 'Bed. Sleeps in the guest room now because the master bedroom feels too empty.' },
