    worry: 'What if Mum falls between now and the move?',
    answer: 'This is the worry that keeps adult children awake more than any other. Over 210,000 over-65s are admitted to hospital each year from falls. We cannot eliminate that risk, but we can shorten the timeline between "thinking about it" and "done."',
  },
  {
    worry: 'I live too far away to help.',
    answer: 'That is exactly why we exist. Your Transition Coordinator is the person on the ground — visiting weekly, coordinating tradespeople, updating you by phone or video. You do not have to take two weeks off work. You do not have to drive three hours every weekend.',
  },
